{"id": "art-28", "label": "Art. 28", "title": "Art. 28", "slug": "art-28", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 28 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_884256188\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2488\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_884256188\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>Adunarea constitutiv&#259; are urm&#259;toarele <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;ii</span>:</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_273734501\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2487\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_273734501\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)verific&#259; <span class=SpellE>existen&#355;a</span>\nv&#259;rs&#259;mintelor;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1009000564\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2486\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1009000564\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)examineaz&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nvalideaz&#259; raportul <span class=SpellE>exper&#355;ilor</span> de evaluare a\naporturilor în natur&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_427339659\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2485\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_427339659\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)aprob&#259; particip&#259;rile la profit ale fondatorilor\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunile</span>\nîncheiate în contul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2006041349\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2484\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2006041349\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)discut&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\naprob&#259; actul constitutiv al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\nmembrii <span class=SpellE>prezen&#355;i</span> reprezentând, în acest scop, <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> pe cei <span class=SpellE>absen&#355;i</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> îi desemneaz&#259; pe aceia care se vor prezenta\npentru autentificarea actului <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> îndeplinirea <span\nclass=SpellE>formalit&#259;&#355;ilor</span> cerute pentru constituirea <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1024603688\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2483\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1024603688\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)<span class=SpellE>nume&#351;te</span> primii membri ai\nconsiliului de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>, respectiv ai\nconsiliului de supraveghere, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> primii cenzori\nsau, dup&#259; caz, primul auditor financiar.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}